<createdBy>nuvolia</createdBy>
<createdTime>2025-09-23 06:30:35 UTC</createdTime>
<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[Balance sheet recognised financial asset instrument obtained by taking possession is an asset that was not pledged by the debtor as collatera or was pledged by the debtor as collaterall, but was  obtained in exchange for the cancellation of debt, whether on a voluntary basis or as part of legal proceedings. ]]></commentInRDBMS>
